snippet.title: Slime Rancher - Holiday Yule Log
snippet.description:
Grab a mug of honey slime tea and relax by our Holiday Yule Log. Help us celebrate another year of ranching on the Far, Far Range!

Music from Slime Rancher's Original Soundtrack II
Listen here: monomipark.bandcamp.com

Play Slime Rancher's Wiggly Wonderland event between Dec 18 - 30
Learn more: http://forums.monomipark.com/viewtopic.php?f=10&t=10334


Follow us to stay up to date on news and events!
http://www.twitter.com/monomipark
http://www.instagram.com/monomi_park


Slime Rancher is developed by Monomi Park
